{"tid":1430791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以色列探月「創世紀號」墜毁　水熊蟲料月球存活","createTime":"2019-08-07T23:37:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T06:04:09.000Z","uid":32934,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a47734a081b813d8bad6bb23c70db0499081a438","tid":1430791,"uid":32934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T23:37:53.000Z","msg":"以色列私營登月探測器「創世紀號」（Beresheet）4月在月球表面墜毁，有份參與計劃的組織周二（6日）承認，太空船上載有數以千計被譽為地球最強生物、俗稱「水熊蟲」的緩步動物門（Tardigrades）。水熊蟲能抵受輻射、撞擊、低溫和高壓等，甚至能不靠食物生存數年之久。有專家估計這批水熊蟲能在月球存活多年，但相信難以繁衍。<br />\n<br />\n美國非牟利組織「方舟使命基金會」（Arch Mission Foundation）創辦人斯皮瓦克（Nova Spivack）透露，研究人員分析「創世紀」號的軌迹及存放水熊蟲的裝置組合，相信牠們在太空船墜毁後存活機會非常高。他指出，這批水熊蟲已被脫水乾燥，處於人工休眠狀態，然後封存於環氧樹脂（epoxy）的人造琥珀中，未來只要補充水分，就可以復活。水熊蟲的大小不到1毫米，但生命力異常頑強，在150℃高溫及零下272℃低溫都能存活數分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20190807/s00005/1565184442120/%e4%bb%a5%e8%89%b2%e5%88%97%e6%8e%a2%e6%9c%88%e3%80%8c%e5%89%b5%e4%b8%96%e7%b4%80%e8%99%9f%e3%80%8d%e5%a2%9c%e6%af%81-%e6%b0%b4%e7%86%8a%e8%9f%b2%e6%96%99%e6%9c%88%e7%90%83%e5%ad%98%e6%b4%bb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20190807%2Fs00005%2F1565184442120%2F%25e4%25bb%25a5%25e8%2589%25b2%25e5%2588%2597%25e6%258e%25a2%25e6%259c%2588%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%2589%25b5%25e4%25b8%2596%25e7%25b4%2580%25e8%2599%259f%25e3%2580%258d%25e5%25a2%259c%25e6%25af%2581-%25e6%25b0%25b4%25e7%2586%258a%25e8%259f%25b2%25e6%2596%2599%25e6%259c%2588%25e7%2590%2583%25e5%25ad%2598%25e6%25b4%25bb&d=zO4uXE7qxnklPfV4Vu9eJaix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=4e62adb6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20190807%2Fs00005%2F1565184442120%2F%25e4%25bb%25a5%25e8%2589%25b2%25e5%2588%2597%25e6%258e%25a2%25e6%259c%2588%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%2589%25b5%25e4%25b8%2596%25e7%25b4%2580%25e8%2599%259f%25e3%2580%258d%25e5%25a2%259c%25e6%25af%2581-%25e6%25b0%25b4%25e7%2586%258a%25e8%259f%25b2%25e6%2596%2599%25e6%259c%2588%25e7%2590%2583%25e5%25ad%2598%25e6%25b4%25bb&h=c3e49a15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20190807/s00005/1565184442120/%e4%bb%a5%e8%89%b2%e5%88%97%e6%8e%a2%e6%9c%88%e3%80%8c%e5%89%b5%e4%b8%96%e7%b4%80%e8%99%9f%e3%80%8d%e5%a2%9c%e6%af%81-%e6%b0%b4%e7%86%8a%e8%9f%b2%e6%96%99%e6%9c%88%e7%90%83%e5%ad%98%e6%b4%bb</a>"},{"pid":"8d80d6f52e8616dc5140d199c2c7911967f94bb4","tid":1430791,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T23:39:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/phRC5fV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FphRC5fV.png&h=3bbcf6de&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VmhbqfW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVmhbqfW.png&h=f1c25f95&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/08/073854_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F08%2F073854_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png&h=127b19ea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/08/073855_0f6641dea7107721bd03942237f5fc64.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F08%2F073855_0f6641dea7107721bd03942237f5fc64.png&h=a1d38059&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/08/073857_7eafb3b7fae203c9f7fe592f2432af34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F08%2F073857_7eafb3b7fae203c9f7fe592f2432af34.png&h=a62d0f4a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/08/073858_85a1606fcfc9b08c9dc289c763a99128.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F08%2F073858_85a1606fcfc9b08c9dc289c763a99128.pn